      "chinese_simplified": "Taimanin. A former high-ranking executive who served the Nisha Clan, one of the eight branches of the Fuuma Clan. But she now leads an independent faction and controls part of the underworld as a gangster, mainly overseeing gambling dens. She has a cheerful and laid-back personality that many perceive as a bit careless, but she also possesses the ruthlessness expected of someone in her line of work when the situation calls for it.\n\nUses the Evil Eye \"Cyclops\", which allows her to freely manipulate metals. She often carries multiple kunai around herself to toy with her opponents. While her Evil Eye is active, even if she is attacked by metal weapons, the weapons will simply pass through her without harming her. Her weapon of choice is a revolver named \"Gold Power\" which fires special bullets.",
      "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin. A former high-ranking executive who served the Nisha Clan, one of the eight branches of the Fuuma Clan. But she now leads an independent faction and controls part of the underworld as a gangster, mainly overseeing gambling dens. She has a cheerful and laid-back personality that many perceive as a bit careless, but she also possesses the ruthlessness expected of someone in her line of work when the situation calls for it.\n\nUses the Evil Eye \"Cyclops\", which allows her to freely manipulate metals. She often carries multiple kunai around herself to toy with her opponents. While her Evil Eye is active, even if she is attacked by metal weapons, the weapons will simply pass through her without harming her. Her weapon of choice is a revolver named \"Gold Power\" which fires special bullets.",
      "spanish": "Taimanin. A former high-ranking executive who served the Nisha Clan, one of the eight branches of the Fuuma Clan. But she now leads an independent faction and controls part of the underworld as a gangster, mainly overseeing gambling dens. She has a cheerful and laid-back personality that many perceive as a bit careless, but she also possesses the ruthlessness expected of someone in her line of work when the situation calls for it.\n\nUses the Evil Eye \"Cyclops\", which allows her to freely manipulate metals. She often carries multiple kunai around herself to toy with her opponents. While her Evil Eye is active, even if she is attacked by metal weapons, the weapons will simply pass through her without harming her. Her weapon of choice is a revolver named \"Gold Power\" which fires special bullets."
