    "icon": "37_Mitsuki",
    "lore": {
      "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_37",
      "english": "Taimanin, graduate of Gosha Academy. She has been active as an official Taimanin after graduation. She was trusted among class-mates as a student council member, but she was criticized by instructors that she is lazy when it comes to finishing her job. Nowadays, she's making up for her past mistakes by accumulating more and more accomplishments.\n\nDiligent, enjoys drinking tea, reading and sunbathing. Her favorite foods are Sukiyaki and Natto.\n\nAs a Wind Art ninja, she has outstanding power and ability in analyzing. Her other name, the \"Storm Fan,\" comes from her combat style that blows away and tears enemies apart with her main weapon ─ a large fan.",
      "japanese": "Taimanin, graduate of Gosha Academy. She has been active as an official Taimanin after graduation. She was trusted among class-mates as a student council member, but she was criticized by instructors that she is lazy when it comes to finishing her job. Nowadays, she's making up for her past mistakes by accumulating more and more accomplishments.\n\nDiligent, enjoys drinking tea, reading and sunbathing. Her favorite foods are Sukiyaki and Natto.\n\nAs a Wind Art ninja, she has outstanding power and ability in analyzing. Her other name, the \"Storm Fan,\" comes from her combat style that blows away and tears enemies apart with her main weapon ─ a large fan.",
      "korean": "Taimanin, graduate of Gosha Academy. She has been active as an official Taimanin after graduation. She was trusted among class-mates as a student council member, but she was criticized by instructors that she is lazy when it comes to finishing her job. Nowadays, she's making up for her past mistakes by accumulating more and more accomplishments.\n\nDiligent, enjoys drinking tea, reading and sunbathing. Her favorite foods are Sukiyaki and Natto.\n\nAs a Wind Art ninja, she has outstanding power and ability in analyzing. Her other name, the \"Storm Fan,\" comes from her combat style that blows away and tears enemies apart with her main weapon ─ a large fan.",
      "chinese_simplified": "Taimanin, graduate of Gosha Academy. She has been active as an official Taimanin after graduation. She was trusted among class-mates as a student council member, but she was criticized by instructors that she is lazy when it comes to finishing her job. Nowadays, she's making up for her past mistakes by accumulating more and more accomplishments.\n\nDiligent, enjoys drinking tea, reading and sunbathing. Her favorite foods are Sukiyaki and Natto.\n\nAs a Wind Art ninja, she has outstanding power and ability in analyzing. Her other name, the \"Storm Fan,\" comes from her combat style that blows away and tears enemies apart with her main weapon ─ a large fan.",
      "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin, graduate of Gosha Academy. She has been active as an official Taimanin after graduation. She was trusted among class-mates as a student council member, but she was criticized by instructors that she is lazy when it comes to finishing her job. Nowadays, she's making up for her past mistakes by accumulating more and more accomplishments.\n\nDiligent, enjoys drinking tea, reading and sunbathing. Her favorite foods are Sukiyaki and Natto.\n\nAs a Wind Art ninja, she has outstanding power and ability in analyzing. Her other name, the \"Storm Fan,\" comes from her combat style that blows away and tears enemies apart with her main weapon ─ a large fan.",
      "spanish": "Taimanin, graduate of Gosha Academy. She has been active as an official Taimanin after graduation. She was trusted among class-mates as a student council member, but she was criticized by instructors that she is lazy when it comes to finishing her job. Nowadays, she's making up for her past mistakes by accumulating more and more accomplishments.\n\nDiligent, enjoys drinking tea, reading and sunbathing. Her favorite foods are Sukiyaki and Natto.\n\nAs a Wind Art ninja, she has outstanding power and ability in analyzing. Her other name, the \"Storm Fan,\" comes from her combat style that blows away and tears enemies apart with her main weapon ─ a large fan."
    },
