      "english": "Taimanin, a student at Gosha Academy. Regularly reads books in the library on her own. She doesn't talk much and gives off a somewhat mysterious vibe.\n\nOne of the very few users of Wave Art among nature-based ninja arts. She can materialize the natural energy, 'waves', and manifest it in the form of a Guardian, which she controls freely with her powers.",
