      "spanish": "Taimanin. Hails from the Momochi ninja clan, an elite family loyal to the Igawa clan, and is the daughter of Momochi Toyo, an instructor of Taimanin Art.\n\nBecause she spent her entire childhood training rigorously under her father, she has no experience with what most Taimanins would consider \"everyday life.\" Because of this, she harbors a quiet longing for a normal, peaceful life. From a young age, she was trained by her strict father in the \"Momochi Style\" a derivative swordsmanship he developed himself. While her swordsmanship rivals that of Akiyama Rinko, who is a fully licensed master in Ittoryu, she lacks real combat experience and has limited ability to adapt in practical situations."
