      "spanish": "A humanoid weapon that was created from the collaboration of UFS and Demon Realm technology in a research facility of Task Force \"G\". Twin sisters born from an egg injected with genes of various species, Yuphie is the elder, and Sophie is the younger sibling. Among the injected genes, the traits of an Oni are most dominant, with vampiric powers also present. \n\nThe elder sister, Yuphie, possesses special abilities focused on defense and healing, complemented by a quiet personality.  The younger sister, Sophie, is physically adept and specialized for offense, with an energetic nature. Although their roles seem clearly divided, it's said that when Yuphie truly unleashes her power, she displays a ferocity and brutality that even surpasses that of her younger sister."
