      "chinese_traditional": "Former Taimanin. Hailing from a clan that served the Koukawa for generations, Koukawa Asuka decided to join the UFS, and in doing so, she also left the Taimanins. Soon after, she worked with the UFS in developing their enhanced Taimanin suit, and now wears a suit on her missions equipped with a Taima Particle Enhancer to test it on the field.\n\nAs a user of \"Ultimate Awakening\", a supernatural ninja art, she possesses the strength of an ogre, which surpasses that of an ordinary human being. Additionally, by activating the Taima Particle Enhancer built into the Taimanin suit, she can deliver powerful and effective strikes, even if only temporarily, against demons or other demonic beings that possess resistance to physical attacks.",
      "spanish": "Former Taimanin. Hailing from a clan that served the Koukawa for generations, Koukawa Asuka decided to join the UFS, and in doing so, she also left the Taimanins. Soon after, she worked with the UFS in developing their enhanced Taimanin suit, and now wears a suit on her missions equipped with a Taima Particle Enhancer to test it on the field.\n\nAs a user of \"Ultimate Awakening\", a supernatural ninja art, she possesses the strength of an ogre, which surpasses that of an ordinary human being. Additionally, by activating the Taima Particle Enhancer built into the Taimanin suit, she can deliver powerful and effective strikes, even if only temporarily, against demons or other demonic beings that possess resistance to physical attacks."
