      "chinese_simplified": "The founder of Nomad. The first vampire.\n\nBeing the first vampire means that he was born a vampire, unlike a human who is turned into one. He is immortal, with no known weaknesses that are likely to appear in lore, and can even walk in sunlight. He is also known as the \"Daywalker\". \n\nHe can transform into mist or dust and can turn humans into vampires by sucking their blood. He also has an ability called \"Energy Drain\", with which he absorbs the life energy of any living thing he touches.",
