      "english": "Codename \"Type Hero\". A being enhanced with the essence of science to stand against demonic entities. However, she possesses a cold personality, lacking the sense of responsibility one might expect from a hero. Instead, she is more akin to a machine built solely to eliminate beings hostile to humanity.\n\nAs a special weapon, she is equipped with the special blade, \"Shin'i\", forged from special particles, and the ever-deployable shield \"Kamui\". Through genetic modification to withstand Byangi’s subordinates, she boasts physical capabilities several times greater than those of an ordinary human.",
