      "chinese_simplified": "Demon. Half-human, half-tiger. An executive of Yomihara's \"Beast Kingdom\" gang. She's like a younger sister to the Beast Kingdom's leader, Hairo Ichirota. Her looks and behavior seem young, but she has a strong sense of loyalty and justice. She helps discriminated beastmen in many ways.\n\nNormally, she takes the form of a human, but can transform herself into a \"Weretiger\" form. She gains superhuman strength, regenerative ability, and agility in this form, growing sharp teeth and claws that can tear through steel. Her war cry can terrorize the mind and body.",
      "chinese_traditional": "Demon. Half-human, half-tiger. An executive of Yomihara's \"Beast Kingdom\" gang. She's like a younger sister to the Beast Kingdom's leader, Hairo Ichirota. Her looks and behavior seem young, but she has a strong sense of loyalty and justice. She helps discriminated beastmen in many ways.\n\nNormally, she takes the form of a human, but can transform herself into a \"Weretiger\" form. She gains superhuman strength, regenerative ability, and agility in this form, growing sharp teeth and claws that can tear through steel. Her war cry can terrorize the mind and body.",
      "spanish": "Demon. Half-human, half-tiger. An executive of Yomihara's \"Beast Kingdom\" gang. She's like a younger sister to the Beast Kingdom's leader, Hairo Ichirota. Her looks and behavior seem young, but she has a strong sense of loyalty and justice. She helps discriminated beastmen in many ways.\n\nNormally, she takes the form of a human, but can transform herself into a \"Weretiger\" form. She gains superhuman strength, regenerative ability, and agility in this form, growing sharp teeth and claws that can tear through steel. Her war cry can terrorize the mind and body."
