      "spanish": "Taimanin. An executive who serves the Nisha clan, one of the eight branches of the Fuuma clan. Although hailing from the prestigious Kuroki clan, renowned for producing brave and steadfast individuals over the years, she stands out as an anomaly with her small stature and bright, graceful appearance. Nevertheless, her natural physical abilities and keen instincts have earned her the reputation of a “genius of combat,” allowing her to excel as an elite ninja.\n\nShe is a user of the Evil Eye known as the “Blind Crimson Serpent Eye.” When activated, “drops of darkness” bubble up from her shadow, concealing part or all of her body. By freely and swiftly manipulating them, she can hide portions of her body to evade enemy attacks, or, for example, launch an assault by manifesting her right arm from drops of darkness that have landed behind her foe—employing unorthodox yet highly adaptable tactics."
