      "chinese_simplified": "A UFS scientist and engineer. She is regarded as the greatest genius in UFS history and an expert in weapon development. Her intellect and engineering prowess are widely recognized within the UFS, and she holds the position of Chief Developer for special weapons. However, her tendency to burn through funds like water in the name of research has become a constant headache for the upper ranks of the UFS.\n\nHer combat ability without assistance is actually below that of an average person. Because of this, she secretly built an android named \"Pamela Jäger\" to support her in both combat and everyday life. She also pilots her custom-built robot, \"General Halloween\", through which she engages in activities proclaiming herself a champion of justice.",
      "chinese_traditional": "A UFS scientist and engineer. She is regarded as the greatest genius in UFS history and an expert in weapon development. Her intellect and engineering prowess are widely recognized within the UFS, and she holds the position of Chief Developer for special weapons. However, her tendency to burn through funds like water in the name of research has become a constant headache for the upper ranks of the UFS.\n\nHer combat ability without assistance is actually below that of an average person. Because of this, she secretly built an android named \"Pamela Jäger\" to support her in both combat and everyday life. She also pilots her custom-built robot, \"General Halloween\", through which she engages in activities proclaiming herself a champion of justice.",
