      "chinese_simplified": "An android created by Rene, the greatest genius scientist in UFS history. Using the body of a female soldier who was near death as the base, her head and torso were preserved in their human form, while the rest of her body was reconstructed with mechanical parts.\n\nHer cybernetic limbs can be swapped out depending on the mission. In everyday situations, she is equipped with lightweight android limbs, serving as Rene's support. In combat, however, she fights in a full‑armor configuration loaded with weapons across her entire body.",
      "chinese_traditional": "An android created by Rene, the greatest genius scientist in UFS history. Using the body of a female soldier who was near death as the base, her head and torso were preserved in their human form, while the rest of her body was reconstructed with mechanical parts.\n\nHer cybernetic limbs can be swapped out depending on the mission. In everyday situations, she is equipped with lightweight android limbs, serving as Rene's support. In combat, however, she fights in a full‑armor configuration loaded with weapons across her entire body.",
      "spanish": "An android created by Rene, the greatest genius scientist in UFS history. Using the body of a female soldier who was near death as the base, her head and torso were preserved in their human form, while the rest of her body was reconstructed with mechanical parts.\n\nHer cybernetic limbs can be swapped out depending on the mission. In everyday situations, she is equipped with lightweight android limbs, serving as Rene's support. In combat, however, she fights in a full‑armor configuration loaded with weapons across her entire body."
