    "class": "Support",
    "trait": "Venus",
    "icon": "108_Mawari",
    "lore": {
      "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_108",
      "english": "Taimanin. Student at Gosha Academy. In exchange for her ability, she is naturally clumsy and is well‑known around campus for constantly tripping over herself. Even so, she continues to work hard, and everyone in Gosha knows she acts for the sake of those around her—so no one makes fun of her for it.\n\nShe is a user of the Evil Eye known as “White Radiance.” When activated, it slows all targets within her field of vision, a formidable ability. However, its effect lasts only a few seconds, and she is unable to move while it is active, making teamwork with allies essential in battle. As a side effect of her power, her perception of time and space becomes temporarily distorted, and even after the effect ends, the distortion never fully disappears.",
      "japanese": "Taimanin. Student at Gosha Academy. In exchange for her ability, she is naturally clumsy and is well‑known around campus for constantly tripping over herself. Even so, she continues to work hard, and everyone in Gosha knows she acts for the sake of those around her—so no one makes fun of her for it.\n\nShe is a user of the Evil Eye known as “White Radiance.” When activated, it slows all targets within her field of vision, a formidable ability. However, its effect lasts only a few seconds, and she is unable to move while it is active, making teamwork with allies essential in battle. As a side effect of her power, her perception of time and space becomes temporarily distorted, and even after the effect ends, the distortion never fully disappears.",
      "korean": "Taimanin. Student at Gosha Academy. In exchange for her ability, she is naturally clumsy and is well‑known around campus for constantly tripping over herself. Even so, she continues to work hard, and everyone in Gosha knows she acts for the sake of those around her—so no one makes fun of her for it.\n\nShe is a user of the Evil Eye known as “White Radiance.” When activated, it slows all targets within her field of vision, a formidable ability. However, its effect lasts only a few seconds, and she is unable to move while it is active, making teamwork with allies essential in battle. As a side effect of her power, her perception of time and space becomes temporarily distorted, and even after the effect ends, the distortion never fully disappears.",
      "chinese_simplified": "Taimanin. Student at Gosha Academy. In exchange for her ability, she is naturally clumsy and is well‑known around campus for constantly tripping over herself. Even so, she continues to work hard, and everyone in Gosha knows she acts for the sake of those around her—so no one makes fun of her for it.\n\nShe is a user of the Evil Eye known as “White Radiance.” When activated, it slows all targets within her field of vision, a formidable ability. However, its effect lasts only a few seconds, and she is unable to move while it is active, making teamwork with allies essential in battle. As a side effect of her power, her perception of time and space becomes temporarily distorted, and even after the effect ends, the distortion never fully disappears.",
      "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin. Student at Gosha Academy. In exchange for her ability, she is naturally clumsy and is well‑known around campus for constantly tripping over herself. Even so, she continues to work hard, and everyone in Gosha knows she acts for the sake of those around her—so no one makes fun of her for it.\n\nShe is a user of the Evil Eye known as “White Radiance.” When activated, it slows all targets within her field of vision, a formidable ability. However, its effect lasts only a few seconds, and she is unable to move while it is active, making teamwork with allies essential in battle. As a side effect of her power, her perception of time and space becomes temporarily distorted, and even after the effect ends, the distortion never fully disappears.",
      "spanish": "Taimanin. Student at Gosha Academy. In exchange for her ability, she is naturally clumsy and is well‑known around campus for constantly tripping over herself. Even so, she continues to work hard, and everyone in Gosha knows she acts for the sake of those around her—so no one makes fun of her for it.\n\nShe is a user of the Evil Eye known as “White Radiance.” When activated, it slows all targets within her field of vision, a formidable ability. However, its effect lasts only a few seconds, and she is unable to move while it is active, making teamwork with allies essential in battle. As a side effect of her power, her perception of time and space becomes temporarily distorted, and even after the effect ends, the distortion never fully disappears."
    },
