      "spanish": "Taimanin, Gosha Academy student. She is from an orphanage where children of Taimanins who were killed or missing in missions are gathered. She helps the owner of the orphanage to take care of those children and supports it financially with the money she earns from her missions. She can't even speak properly with people apart from the kids at the orphanage, so she brings up her alter ego on missions by wearing a mask.\n\nHer ninja art is Mirror Art that controls Particles by using a mirror as a catalyst and copying other ninja arts or demonic natures of those who were reflected in it. Preparations are a must since it has many limitations, but as it has infinite potential, it is used as a secret weapon."
