      "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin. She's a daughter of one of the most prestigious Taimanin clans, the Inokura clan. Well-mannered, but is shy about voicing her opinion. Although she's timid, she's affectionate towards her teammates and has a loving personality.\n\nHowever, behind her timidness is a perverse side that feels pleasure in seeing her enemies quiver in fear. As one of the radical Taimanin clans, she thoroughly exterminates demons and trains hard, striving to create a relationship of non-aggression that will last for centuries.\n\nShe uses a special ninja art called Scarlet Art. When entering a scarlet fog created by her ninja art \"Scarlet Miasma\", you can't distinguish friends from foes and will kill your allies instead of your enemies. What's worse is that the effects aren't the same every time and are ineffective to some, and will cause disputes and tragic accidents. She is feared as The Scarlet Lady as she is caked with blood and ecstatically watches over her enemies flailing in the scarlet fog she created.",
