      "chinese_simplified": "Taimanin. A student of Gosha Academy. She uses Stone Art to cover her body with stones or to capture enemies.\n\nIt is said that some people among her predecessors were able to make a giant doll made of rock, a golem. Although she has yet to achieve the level of her predecessors, she works hard every day to be a great Stone Art user like them.\n\nAkina is a ramen maniac. She always goes to a ramen store after a hard mission or training session to release stress by eating ramen.",
      "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin. A student of Gosha Academy. She uses Stone Art to cover her body with stones or to capture enemies.\n\nIt is said that some people among her predecessors were able to make a giant doll made of rock, a golem. Although she has yet to achieve the level of her predecessors, she works hard every day to be a great Stone Art user like them.\n\nAkina is a ramen maniac. She always goes to a ramen store after a hard mission or training session to release stress by eating ramen.",
      "spanish": "Taimanin. A student of Gosha Academy. She uses Stone Art to cover her body with stones or to capture enemies.\n\nIt is said that some people among her predecessors were able to make a giant doll made of rock, a golem. Although she has yet to achieve the level of her predecessors, she works hard every day to be a great Stone Art user like them.\n\nAkina is a ramen maniac. She always goes to a ramen store after a hard mission or training session to release stress by eating ramen."
