      "chinese_simplified": "Demon. An executive of \"Kibushu\" or \"Oni Warrior Horde\", one of the major crime syndicates in Tokyo Kingdom. Has a strict personality and a competitive spirit, always looking forward to matches against pwerful individuals. At the same time, she shows a diligent side, often taking care of her fellow teammates or execuitivers.\n\nAs a sorceress, she specializes in wind magic. Repels enemy attacks with violent storms and can even blow away her opponents, tearing them to shreds. Not only can she summon raging storms, but she can also stir up light breezes, freely demonstrating delicate and precise control of the wind.",
      "chinese_traditional": "Demon. An executive of \"Kibushu\" or \"Oni Warrior Horde\", one of the major crime syndicates in Tokyo Kingdom. Has a strict personality and a competitive spirit, always looking forward to matches against pwerful individuals. At the same time, she shows a diligent side, often taking care of her fellow teammates or execuitivers.\n\nAs a sorceress, she specializes in wind magic. Repels enemy attacks with violent storms and can even blow away her opponents, tearing them to shreds. Not only can she summon raging storms, but she can also stir up light breezes, freely demonstrating delicate and precise control of the wind.",
      "spanish": "Demon. An executive of \"Kibushu\" or \"Oni Warrior Horde\", one of the major crime syndicates in Tokyo Kingdom. Has a strict personality and a competitive spirit, always looking forward to matches against pwerful individuals. At the same time, she shows a diligent side, often taking care of her fellow teammates or execuitivers.\n\nAs a sorceress, she specializes in wind magic. Repels enemy attacks with violent storms and can even blow away her opponents, tearing them to shreds. Not only can she summon raging storms, but she can also stir up light breezes, freely demonstrating delicate and precise control of the wind."
